    {
      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-800f-a05b-c9338e7a79bc",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The recommender estimates the knowledge level of the learner and makes recommendations based on learner preferences and knowledge level and predicts the time it will take the learner to learn and how he/she will perform. Performance of the model is assessed using R-Squared. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-800f-a05b-c9338e7a79bc",
        "parent": {
